**Events**

- **A Holiday Evening in the Village**: On December 6, 2025, the Historic Village hosted "A Holiday Evening in the Village," featuring visits with Mrs. Claus, storytelling by the fireplace, and sing-alongs in The School Section School, complete with homemade cookies. ([cityofrichmond.net](https://www.cityofrichmond.net/DocumentCenter/View/3694/Holiday-Evening-in-the-Village-2025?utm_source=openai))

